SELECT u.username, d.device_name, i.event_type FROM users u JOIN devices d ON u.id = d.user_id JOIN interactions i ON d.device_id = i.device_id WHERE u.age < 40;
SELECT u.username, COUNT(r.result_id) AS total_results FROM users u LEFT JOIN recognition_results r ON u.id = r.user_id GROUP BY u.username ORDER BY total_results DESC;

SELECT u.username, d.device_name, i.event_type, r.match_score FROM users u JOIN devices d ON u.id = d.user_id JOIN interactions i ON d.device_id = i.device_id JOIN recognition_results r ON u.id = r.user_id AND d.device_id = r.device_id ORDER BY r.match_score DESC;
